station of her ward by unidentified senior students in the school. December 29, 2020 In "News" Akwa Ibom State government said it has transferred the case of master Don Davis allegedly molested at the Deeper Life High School, Uyo, to the police for a more discreet investigation. December 31, 2020 In "Education" By Chioma Onuegbu - Uyo Parents of 11-year-old Don-Davies Archibong, JSS1 student of Deeper Life High School, Idoro Uyo, have demanded the sum of one hundred million naira compensation for the inhuman torture their son was allegedly subjected to in the school. This is contained in a letter addressed to… January 1, 2021 In "Metro"